[OVERLAY] VimFu — :%s/old/new/g — Whole File
[SAY] Percent S is the most common way to do find and replace across an entire file.
[SAY] The word foo appears on several lines. Let's rename it to bar everywhere.
[TYPE] ':%s/foo/bar/g'

